_sText:
Surf_Wazor Counterstrike: Source Skill-Surf map. Created in association with Mirror Map Studios with productive help by Krusty.
Map information:
Surf_Wazor contains 5 stages which go from skilllevel easy to hard. You have 5 minutes to beat all levels. If nobody has reached the end in the given time the players will spawn in a Scout-Map and fight to death. Made for 66 Tick and sv_airaccelerate 150 Noblock required!
Credits
Level one made by: Krusty, Junior Level two made by: Amstaff Level three made by: Amstaff Level four made by: Krusty, Junior Level five made by: Amstaff Jails made by: Mike999 Jetpack made by: Caterpillar Thanks to all map testers, such as Mirror Mapping Studios with bug reports and gameplay tips!
